OL,3,CMore droughts declared in England: How
OL,4,Cwill it affect you?
OL,6,FFour areas of England are now
OL,7,Fofficially in drought and authorities
OL,8,Fare warning more regions could follow
OL,9,Fbefore the end of summer.
OL,11,FIt comes after England recorded its
OL,12,Fdriest spring in more than 100 years
OL,13,Fand warmest June on record.
OL,15,FRainfall has been 'exceptionally low'
OL,16,Ffor consecutive months, and many
OL,17,Frivers are experiencing levels as low
OL,18,Fas previous major droughts, putting
OL,19,Freservoirs under pressure.
