OL,3,CMore droughts declared in England: How
OL,4,Cwill it affect you?
OL,6,FHosepipe bans have been enacted in
OL,7,Fseveral areas, and more places are
OL,8,Flikely to join. So, is your area at
OL,9,Frisk, and how will the drought affect
OL,10,Fyou?
OL,12,FWhy is a drought declared?
OL,14,FThe decision to declare a drought
OL,15,Fhappens when there has not been enough
OL,16,Frain and water levels in reservoirs
OL,17,Fdrop to exceptionally low levels.
