OL,3,CMore droughts declared in England: How
OL,4,Cwill it affect you?
OL,6,FThere is no single definition of
OL,7,Fdrought, as every drought is
OL,8,Fdifferent, according to the
OL,9,FEnvironment Agency.
OL,11,FBut it's the Environment Agency that
OL,12,Fdecides to declare a drought in
OL,13,Fparticular areas of England based on
OL,14,Freservoir levels, water flow in
OL,15,Frivers, weather outlook and the
OL,16,Fdryness of the ground and soil.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
