OL,3,CMore droughts declared in England: How
OL,4,Cwill it affect you?
OL,6,FA drought is officially declared so
OL,7,Fthat water companies and other bodies
OL,8,Fimplement drought action plans and
OL,9,Fprotocols to shore up drinking water
OL,10,Fsupplies.
OL,12,FWhat areas are in drought?
OL,14,FThe East and West Midlands, the North
OL,15,FWest and Yorkshire are all officially
OL,16,Fin drought.
OL,18,FBut most of England is in a status of
OL,19,Fprolonged dry weather, which is the
OL,20,Flevel just below drought.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
