OL,3,CMore droughts declared in England: How
OL,4,Cwill it affect you?
OL,6,FThe Mid and South Ceredigion area in
OL,7,Fwest Wales is considered to be
OL,8,F"developing drought" and eastern
OL,9,FScotland - which does not declare
OL,10,Fdrought - is considered to have
OL,11,F"moderate" water scarcity levels.
OL,13,FAre there more areas at risk of
OL,14,Fdrought?
OL,16,FYes, the Environment Agency has warned
OL,17,Fthat more regions are likely to enter
OL,18,Fofficial drought status by September.
