OL,3,CMore droughts declared in England: How
OL,4,Cwill it affect you?
OL,6,FIt says if England gets 80% of its
OL,7,Flong-term average rainfall and warmer
OL,8,Ftemperatures over the next few weeks,
OL,9,Feight areas could be declared in
OL,10,Fdrought by the end of summer.
OL,12,FThat could include Thames Wessex,
OL,13,Fparts of the Solent and South Downs,
OL,14,Fparts of East Anglia and Lincolnshire
OL,15,Fand Northamptonshire.
