OL,3,CMore droughts declared in England: How
OL,4,Cwill it affect you?
OL,6,FWater companies will often introduce
OL,7,Fhosepipe bans - or temporary use bans
OL,8,F- to restrict water use.
OL,10,FUnder these rules, customers cannot
OL,11,Fuse hosepipes, including for cleaning
OL,12,Fcars, watering gardens or allotments,
OL,13,Ffilling paddling pools and swimming
OL,14,Fpools or cleaning windows.
OL,16,FYet, some areas that are in drought
OL,17,Fdon't have a hosepipe ban in place and
OL,18,Fothers, like Oxfordshire, Kent and
OL,19,FSussex, which are not officially in
OL,20,Fdrought, do.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
