OL,4,Cwill it affect you?
OL,6,FUnder drought management conditions,
OL,7,Fwater companies will also have to fix
OL,8,Fleaks and adjust operations to
OL,9,Fconserve more water.
OL,11,FAuthorities are urging all people
OL,12,Facross England to use water wisely,
OL,13,Fwhether an official ban is in place or
OL,14,Fnot.
