OL,3,CMore droughts declared in England: How
OL,4,Cwill it affect you?
OL,6,FThe situation for farmers has been
OL,7,Fdeteriorating. Some farmers have
OL,8,Freported failing and poorer quality
OL,9,Fcrops because of the drought
OL,10,Fconditions. This could lead to
OL,11,Fshortages of certain fruit and
OL,12,Fvegetables, which in turn could
OL,13,Fincrease prices.
OL,15,FLivestock yields could also be
OL,16,Faffected as a result of low rainfall
OL,17,Fand reduced grass growth, which means
OL,18,Fwinter feed supplies could be affected
OL,19,Flater in the year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
