OL,3,CMore droughts declared in England: How
OL,4,Cwill it affect you?
OL,6,FDairy farmers have also reported
OL,7,Fhaving to use feed for their cattle
OL,8,Fthis summer as there is no pasture to
OL,9,Fgraze on.
OL,11,FThe National Drought Group, which
OL,12,Fincludes the National Farmers Union,
OL,13,Fsays it is working to support farmers
OL,14,Fand growers with access to water.
OL,16,FWhat is the environmental impact?
OL,18,FDroughts generally have an enormous
OL,19,Fimpact on the environment, wildlife
OL,20,Fand waterways.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
