OL,3,CMore droughts declared in England: How
OL,4,Cwill it affect you?
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency has already
OL,7,Fcarried out several fish rescues this
OL,8,Fsummer as the higher temperatures are
OL,9,Fcausing more fish to die off than
OL,10,Fusual.
OL,12,FThere have also been blue-green algae
OL,13,Fblooms detected in waterways, which
OL,14,Fcan be harmful to ecosystems, pets and
OL,15,Fpeople using the water.
OL,17,FDrought also brings increased wildfire
OL,18,Frisk due to the hot, dry conditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
