OL,11,FWhen will we get out of the drought?
OL,13,FThere is no clear picture on the long-
OL,14,Fterm weather outlook, according to the
OL,15,FMet Office's chief meteorologist, Will
OL,16,FLang.
OL,18,F"The most likely situation is that we
OL,19,Fwill have somewhere near average
OL,20,Frainfall for the UK and also for
OL,21,FEngland and Wales as a whole," he said.
