OL,3,CMore droughts declared in England: How
OL,4,Cwill it affect you?
OL,6,FBut even if there is rainfall during a
OL,7,Fdrought, or even a flash flood, it
OL,8,Fdoesn't mean the drought is over.
OL,9,FEnough rain needs to fall to replenish
OL,10,Fgroundwater reserves, reservoirs and
OL,11,Frivers to remove restrictions and
OL,12,Fdrought status, and that can take a
OL,13,Flong time.
